Package ui.appointments

package ui.appointments
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AppointmentAddPage
    AppointmentAddPage is the pop-up displayed in the application for adding a new appointment.
    AppointmentAddPageButtons
    AppointmentAddPageButtons are the submit and cancel buttons on the add appointment form.
    AppointmentEditPage
    AppointmentEditPage is the pop-up displayed to edit an appointment in the application
    AppointmentEditPageButtons
    AppointmentEditPageButtons are the submit and cancel buttons on the edit appointment form.
    AppointmentInfoForm
    AppointmentInfoForm contains the fields for adding or updating an Appointment.
    AppointmentTableControls
    AppointmentTableControls contains the buttons for interacting with the data stored in the table.
    AppointmentTablePane
    AppointmentTablePane contains the buttons and tableview displayed in the application for appointments.
    AppointmentTableView
    AppointmentTableView displays a table containing all appointment documents stored in the database.
